---
const without = [
  'Fifty disconnected SaaS tools, each with its own login',
  'Identity scattered across every vendor directory',
  'Audit trails that don\'t reconcile across systems',
  'Access governance debt nobody owns',
  'Half a dozen support contracts at 2am',
  'Compliance posture only as strong as the weakest vendor',
];

const withG8 = [
  'One integrated platform, one operations model',
  'Identity governed once through G8ID',
  'Unified audit trail through g8audit',
  'Joiner-mover-leaver wired through the spine',
  'One vendor, one contract, one accountability chain',
  'Compliance posture inherited by every product',
];
---

<section id="problem" class="section bg-surface">
  <div class="container-page">
    <header class="max-w-4xl">
      <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-sky-400">
        The problem
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
        Most organisations don't have a software problem.<br class="hidden sm:block" />
        They have a software <span class="text-sky-400">sprawl</span> problem.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-600">
        Two decades of procurement-led tool adoption left regulated organisations with seams nobody owns and a compliance posture that's only as strong as the weakest vendor on the stack.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8">
      <article class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-surface-soft p-7 lg:p-9">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-400">
            <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-300 text-ink-400">
              <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M2 2l6 6M8 2l-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            Without g8suite
          </p>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-ink-400">Today's reality</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-navy-900">Tool sprawl, vendor sprawl, audit sprawl</h3>

        <!-- Fragmentation diagram -->
        <svg
          viewBox="0 0 360 160"
          class="mt-6 h-auto w-full"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <g stroke="#94A3B8" stroke-width="1" fill="none">
            {[...Array(20).keys()].map((i) => {
              const x1 = (i * 17 + 10) % 340 + 10;
              const y1 = (i * 41) % 130 + 15;
              const x2 = ((i + 7) * 19) % 340 + 10;
              const y2 = ((i + 3) * 37) % 130 + 15;
              return <line x1={x1} y1={y1} x2={x2} y2={y2} stroke-dasharray="2 3" opacity="0.5" />;
            })}
          </g>
          <g>
            {[...Array(14).keys()].map((i) => {
              const x = (i * 27 + 18) % 340 + 8;
              const y = (i * 43) % 130 + 15;
              return (
                <g>
                  <rect x={x} y={y} width="32" height="18" rx="3" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#94A3B8" stroke-width="1" />
                </g>
              );
            })}
          </g>
        </svg>

        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
          {without.map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-600">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-ink-400" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M4 4l8 8M12 4l-8 8" stroke-linecap="round" />
              </svg>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-navy-900/15 bg-navy-900 p-7 text-white lg:p-9">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-sky-400">
            <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-green/15 text-accent-green">
              <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M2 5.5l2 2L8 3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            With g8suite
          </p>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-sky-100/80">One platform</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white">One spine. One audit. One vendor.</h3>

        <!-- Consolidation diagram -->
        <svg
          viewBox="0 0 360 160"
          class="mt-6 h-auto w-full"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <!-- Central hub -->
          <rect x="150" y="60" width="60" height="40" rx="6" fill="#1E3A6F" stroke="#7BB3E8" stroke-width="1" />
          <text x="180" y="84" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" fill="#7BB3E8" font-weight="600">SPINE</text>

          <!-- Orbit nodes -->
          {[
            { x: 40, y: 30 },
            { x: 320, y: 30 },
            { x: 40, y: 130 },
            { x: 320, y: 130 },
            { x: 30, y: 80 },
            { x: 330, y: 80 },
          ].map((p) => (
            <g>
              <line x1="180" y1="80" x2={p.x + 16} y2={p.y + 9} stroke="#7BB3E8" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2 3" opacity="0.7" />
              <rect x={p.x} y={p.y} width="32" height="18" rx="3" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#7BB3E8" stroke-width="1" />
            </g>
          ))}
        </svg>

        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
          {withG8.map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-sky-100/90">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-accent-green" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M3 8l3.5 3.5L13 4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-sky-400 bg-sky-100/40 p-7 lg:p-8">
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-navy-900 lg:text-lg">
        The answer is not more integrations. The answer is consolidation on a platform built for sovereignty from the ground up.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
